aes::semantic(traversal_on_permission)

  × cannot traverse through a computed permission
   ╭─[test.aes:4:15]
 3 │   def read = .owner;
 4 │   def view = .read.view;
   ·               ──┬─
   ·                 ╰── this is a `def`, but traversals require a `let` relation
